        Inclusion Criteria:

        -

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  neurological, vascular and musculoskeletal disorders of the lower and upper limbs;

          -  being on pharmacological therapy related to either neural and/or vascular response,
             including hormonal contraceptives and oral supplements;

          -  being a current or former smoker;

          -  having an irregular menstrual cycle (26 to 35 days) up to 3 months before the
             beginning of the study;

          -  contraindications to joint mobilization; regular involvement in a SLKE or PS training
             programme.
